								<p
									class="text-color"
									set:html={t({
										en: 'Our footprint spans key financial hubs, with offices in <b>Dubai</b>, <b>Seychelles</b>, <b>Limassol (Cyprus)</b>, <b>Lagos (Nigeria)</b>, and <b>Malta</b>. We are also planning to expand further into Latin America and Asia in 2024, extending our reach and delivering the best-regulated brokerage services to a wider audience.',
